<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #FFEDE8;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #E27A82;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #E09E7A;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #E27A82;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #E09E7A;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Inquiry Received</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for reaching out. We have received your inquiry and our admin will get back to you shortly.</p>
            <p>If you have any further questions or need immediate assistance, please feel free to reply to this email or visit our website.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p>Your Therapy Practice Team</p>
            <a href="https://www.yourwebsite.com" class="btn">Visit Our Website</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
